name: Item #00008 Animal
description: Item #00008 Animal is some experimental mark making by Iris on 3rd September 2021. Mainly experimenting with colors etc. she had painted the form of an animal marking out the legs and some form of body, this was quite progressive for her skills at her age. This is NFT number 8 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
